Please leave the Storage Code and EPA WASTE CODE S  fields blank       Once the form has been completed  email the form to chemwaste uic edu     You will be notified via e mail if your request has been accepted or rejected  If your request is rejected  you will be told what corrections or additional information is needed       You will receive a five digit requisition number when your request is accepted  Please refer to this requisition number when inquiring about the status of your request     If you are requesting removal of a Peroxiding compound  please make sure you have tested it recently if you can safely do so   We recommend MQuant Peroxide test strips from Millipore Sigma Millipore Sigma Web Privacy 